msgid "Values"
msgstr "Valeurs"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Mobility**"
msgstr "**Mobilité**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Autonomous · Cane · Walker · Wheelchair · Bedridden"
msgstr "Autonome · Canne · Déambulateur · Fauteuil roulant · Alité"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Continence**"
msgstr "**Continence**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid ""
"Continent · Occasional Incontinence · Frequent Incontinence · Incontinent"
msgstr ""
"Continent · Incontinence occasionnelle · Incontinence fréquente · "
"Incontinent"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Cognitive Status**"
msgstr "**Statut cognitif**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Mild Impairment · Moderate Impairment · Severe Impairment"
msgstr "Normal · Trouble léger · Trouble modéré · Trouble sévère"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Communication**"
msgstr "**Communication**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Difficulty · Non-verbal · Aphasia"
msgstr "Normale · Difficulté · Non verbal · Aphasie"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:103
msgid "Senses and risks"
msgstr "Les sens et les risques"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:105
msgid "The **Senses & Risk Assessment** section completes the profile:"
msgstr "La section **Sens & Évaluation des risques** complète le profil :"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Vision**"
msgstr "**Vision**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Corrected (Glasses) · Impaired · Blind"
msgstr "Normale · Corrigée (lunettes) · Diminuée · Aveugle"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Hearing**"
msgstr "**Audition**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Hearing Aid · Impaired · Deaf"
msgstr "Normale · Appareil auditif · Diminuée · Sourd"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Fall Risk**"
msgstr "**Risque de chute**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Yes / No"
msgstr "Oui / Non"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Pressure Sore Risk**"
msgstr "**Risque d'escarre**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Low · Moderate · High"
msgstr "Faible · Modéré · Élevé"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:114
msgid "These indicators guide daily monitoring and feed into the care plan."
msgstr ""
"Ces indicateurs orientent la surveillance quotidienne et alimentent le plan "
"de soins."

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:116
msgid "Medical devices"
msgstr "Les dispositifs médicaux"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:118
msgid ""
"The **Medical Devices** section lists the devices and permanent conditions:"
msgstr ""
"La section **Dispositifs médicaux** recense les dispositifs et conditions "
"permanentes :"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:120
msgid "**Urinary Catheter** (yes / no);"
msgstr "**Sonde urinaire** (oui / non) ;"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:121
msgid "**Stoma** (yes / no);"
msgstr "**Stomie** (oui / non) ;"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:122
msgid ""
"**Dental Status**: Natural Teeth · Partial Denture · Full Denture · "
"Edentulous."
msgstr ""
"**État dentaire** : Dents naturelles · Prothèse partielle · Prothèse "
"complète · Édenté."

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:125
msgid "Diagnoses (ICD-10 pathologies)"
msgstr "Les diagnostics (pathologies CIM-10)"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:127
msgid ""
"The **Diagnoses / Pathologies** section lists the resident's pathologies, "
"coded according to **ICD-10** (International Classification of Diseases). "
"Each line links the resident to a pathology from the **catalog**."
msgstr ""
"La section **Diagnostics / Pathologies** liste les pathologies du résident, "
"codées selon la **CIM-10** (classification internationale des maladies). "
"Chaque ligne relie le résident à une pathologie du **catalogue**."

